data.description: Welcome to this spacious and beautifully appointed 5BR/4.5BA home in Murabella situated on a generous 0.35-acre lot. With just over 3300 sf, you have plenty of space to spread out inside and outside. Inside is designed with 3BR/3.5BA (including the master) on the first floor, 1BR/1BA upstairs bedroom suite and a 1BR/1BA first floor In-Law suite with it's own exterior entry as well as interior access. As you enter through the front door, you'll immediately be captivated by the seamless flow of the living spaces. The heart of this home is the kitchen, anchoring the living space with the living room, the formal and casual dining spaces and kitchen flowing seamlessly together making entertaining a breeze. Center-open sliders off the living room lead to the lush and expansive backyard that is fully fenced and offers endless opportunities for outdoor activities, gardening, and relaxation. Center-open sliders off the living room lead to the lush and expansive backyard that is fully fenced and offers endless opportunities for outdoor activities, gardening, and relaxation. Back inside, the kitchen overlooks the living space offering plenty of cabinets and counter space, SS appliances and a large corner pantry to keep everything you need at hand. The master suite, located at the rear of the home, provides a private oasis. With its spacious layout, it offers a tranquil retreat with an en-suite bathroom that includes a dual vanity and garden tub to help you relax at the end of your day. On the opposite end of the house, you'll find two well-appointed bedrooms that share a Jack and Jill bathroom, perfect for children or guests. These rooms are beautifully lit and offer plenty of space and comfort. Ascending the stairs, you'll discover a versatile loft/bedroom area with its own walk-in closet and bathroom. This versatile space can serve as a guest suite, home office, or playroom, allowing for flexibility to meet your needs. One of the standout features of this property is the mother-in-law suite located on the main level, complete with a private entrance. This self-contained living space includes a convenient kitchenette, a comfortable bedroom, and an en-suite bathroom, offering guests or extended family members a cozy and independent living experience. Murabella offers tons of amenities including a community pool, a clubhouse, tennis courts and more. Located in the World Golf Village area gives you access to shopping, restaurants, and with the I-95 nearby, your never far from beaches or the city. Welcome home!
